name: Selasar_Imajinasi Tarot #II "The High Priestess"
description:
II - La Papesse
It is one of the 22 Major Arcana
by Selasar Imajinasi.

She was a priestess who was hundreds of years old but had a childlike youthful appearance.
Even though she was small, there was a divine presence that resided within her.
